com.thomsonreuters.upa.codec

Interface PostUserInfo


  • public interface PostUserInfo
    The PostUserInfo contains information that identifies the user posting this information. If present on a RefreshMsg, this implies that this refresh was posted to the system by the user described in postUserInfo.
    See Also:
    PostMsg, RefreshMsg, StatusMsg, UpdateMsg
